@startuml processing-page-structure
start
:Display "Processing Page";
:Show circular progress indicator;
:Display message "Processing your document, please wait...";
note right
  The circular progress indicator and
  message inform the user that the system
  is processing the document.
end note

if (Processing complete?) then (yes)
  :Navigate to success page or display success message;
  stop
else (no)
  :Handle processing error or timeout;
  note right
    If an error occurs, display an appropriate
    message or provide an option to retry.
  end note
  stop
endif

@enduml
